name: The Resonant Forest
description:
Still quietness reigns in the Resonant Forest.
Not a sound can be heard, not even that of its trees rustling or living beings walking on its dark soil.
The absolute silence can be maddening, but any attempt to put an end to it is pointless.
No sound shall ever be heard in the Resonant Forest, be it the trees rustling, steps on the soil or cries of pure despair.
